UML:UseCase.name: Contribution to the Service/Service Provider appreciation

UML:TaggedValue.value: Contribution to the Service/Service Provider appreciation

The end users can express their satisfaction with the help received on the reported problem. This evaluation contributes to the evaluation of the Service and Service Provider shown on the Service page at uStore

In order to ensure higher user satisfaction, the ticket could be sent to multiple service providers/developers that can handle the request
The TS should support setting deadlines for completing the tickets and the deelopers/service providers working on given ticket should be able to report the progress
